item.title: Can you give me your code
item.description: Only one person can correctly interpret it as it is based off a personal anecdote. He knows that. can you give me your code, if you like it as it is, just a java file, jittery with small classes and big functions, which I anyways don’t care much about, after all it is the java file I need. The java file you dearly need, petrified the strings holding my skull together
